WHO   — The Dark One — the imprisoned source of the Shadow
WHAT  — Shai'tan, the imprisoned antithesis of the Creator — the force of entropy, chaos, and unmaking.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: The Shadow — the imprisoned source outside the Pattern  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — His unmaking presses against the Pattern itself, and to free him would end the turning of the Wheel.
HOW   — Sealed outside time at creation; his prison breaches and reseals across the Ages, his touch tainting and corrupting.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Outside time he presses, and to speak his name is to draw his eye.

